02:50:48,863 --> 02:50:49,529
<b>Um corvo!</b>

2126
02:50:50,448 --> 02:50:51,240
<b>Os pássaros...</b>

2127
02:50:51,491 --> 02:50:53,492
<b>estão voltando para a montanha.</b>

2128
02:50:56,913 --> 02:50:58,664
<b>Meu caro Óin...</b>

2129
02:50:58,915 --> 02:51:00,666
